reviewText: I can understand folks who would pay a hefty sum for Wizard Video big box and other extremely rare VHS items, but there is absolutely nothing valuable or rare about these four tapes. VHS hasn't been in production since 2006 but you could easily find any of these tapes at a second hand store or thrift shop. As the other reviewer stated, some of these vendors have bricks in their heads.
These vendors who think these old 80s movies are worth gold have bricks in their heads. Somebody needs a reality check.
